{"service_name": "Remote Infrastructure Management Service (RIM)", "service_id": "6480585967009792", "company_name": "MTI Technology Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     MTI Technology Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Remote Infrastructure Management Service (RIM)\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    MTI\u2019s Remote Infrastructure Management Service is governed by a framework that delivers proactive monitoring, management and support, alongside detailed analysis of the client\u2019s infrastructure to ensure quick &amp; efficient resolution to issues identified through Enterprise-class end-to-end event, incident, problem, change, performance, capacity and availability management.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     COMPUTE Monitoring, management, support and optimisation of the environment\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Proactive Event notification of component and service utilisation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Incident and Problem Management of VM failure\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Change request to manage process for installing additional hosts\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     STORAGE Remote monitoring, analysis and management of storage and systems\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     NETWORK Monitoring of core switches, routers and SAN fabric\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     BACKUP Full Incident Lifecycle Management of backup\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     SECURITY Support, monitoring and management of security services\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Comprehensive backup &amp; recovery services ensure data protection and compliance\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     SERVICE LEVELS Monitor, Analyse, Manage and Complete\n  